OG-USA.title: Updated the OG-USA PSL_catalog.json
OG-USA.body:
This PR updates the OG-USA `PSL_catalog.json` file according to the new PSLmodels.org catalog requirements (https://github.com/PSLmodels/PSL-Infrastructure/blob/master/Docs/Adding-Projects.md).

@jdebacker you should take a look at this and make sure everything is right. For example, I pointed the URL for your picture at your GitHub profile picture. Let me know if you want me to put a different URL.

openfisca-uk.title: Update National Insurance rates to align with Autumn Update 2023
openfisca-uk.body:
Fixes #824
Fixes #825 
Fixes #826 

This PR updates NIC rates to align with the Autumn Update 2023. It does not deal with any other reforms, if any, introduced by the update. Additionally, it does not write any new tests for the relevant portions of the NIC variable, as tests already exist for them.
